# {{PROJECT_NAME}} — {{LANGUAGE_DISPLAY}} Coding Rules

## Architecture

Layer dependency (unidirectional): `domain` ← `application` ← `infrastructure` ← `presentation`
The `domain` layer must not depend on external libraries. (→ `docs/adr/001`)

## Coding Rules

{{LANGUAGE_RULES}}

